{"tid":451203,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意洗衫舖嘅味?","createTime":"2017-10-29T03:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T04:43:11.000Z","uid":66945,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"baf94393fad0289edd2b7e4c21f27d8cad6a8ea3","tid":451203,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"次次行過都會索大啖啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市面上有冇類似咁嘅味嘅柔順劑/香精?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1b93bbd63bddba158c5e8b709b8d438070376a","tid":451203,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"好香，但自己啲衫永遠洗唔到呢陣又keep得耐又香既味"},{"pid":"7f4de8f3e99d634634a05d30e1f51979aac1f2dd","tid":451203,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"有冇做洗衫舖嘅人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd70c5533120183a05ea3f1fcdbcae96e78164c","tid":451203,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好香，但自己啲衫永遠洗唔到呢陣又keep得耐又香既味</blockquote><br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我洗衫用柔順劑，啲衫乾左都冇咁勁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6d1c70c5159efc82b8763906bae71b14932d85","tid":451203,"uid":28588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"究竟佢地用咩洗衣粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7794747f3ab9c132cd7b68b216ad63828390ac4a","tid":451203,"uid":102475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"我拎衫落街洗<br />\n發覺大汗既話乾左之後d衫有一撻撻唔知係咩既劑既漬<br />\n會唔會係佢地洗完之後特登唔過清d柔順劑<br />\n或者柔順劑本來就唔需要洗甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097ed68d212f4559b97c552c6adcf62397f98008","tid":451203,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟佢地用咩洗衣粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/33497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F33497.jpg&h=c171a0fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8311500c8268e8f30293fa384f43c615428945bc","tid":451203,"uid":12412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"因為乾衣焗一焗啲柔順劑味仲出啲"},{"pid":"08c7b374f1980a918e046068af5b4909e613da23","tid":451203,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我拎衫落街洗<br />\n發覺大汗既話乾左之後d衫有一撻撻唔知係咩既劑既漬<br />\n會唔會係佢地洗完之後特登唔過清d柔順劑<br />\n或者柔順劑本來就唔需要洗甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問佢地點解有漬吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebda08d2e218baaab6ecab867d7f64778b68d17","tid":451203,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"我鐘意戲院味"}]}